{
  "chapter": 18,
  "chapter_summary": "谢玉宝夜不能寐，怀疑买盐的人与陶保义旧日身份有关，可能会危及自己，便以绝食相逼，让马如龙换黑衣蒙面去查。马如龙初探陶保义家一无所获，谢玉宝凭江湖经验指出厨房灶火和无水井才可能藏有暗道秘窟。马如龙再探，发现灶热井枯，正欲离开时被井底买盐的人认出，只得下井。井底除买盐的人外，还有一个枯瘦干裂的吃盐之人，他不断喝水、吃盐、吞生鸡蛋，显出诡异病态。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "喂，你睡着了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你为什么睡不着？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "是不是也在想那个人的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "那个地保既然练过武，你想他以前会不会是个江洋大盗，那个来买盐的人就是他以前的同党，到这里很可能又是在准备计划做件案子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "做案子跟买盐有什么关系？跟我们有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "说不定他们是准备来抢这家杂货店，买盐就是为了来探路！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我们这家杂货店有什么值得别人来抢的东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "有一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "一样什么东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你认为他们要抢你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "也许你是真的不知道我是谁，可是你一定要相信，如果我落入了那些恶人手里……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "虽然我一直猜不透，你为什么要这样对我，可是，这些日子来，我已看出，你不是个坏人，所以，你一定要帮我去查出那个人的来历。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我怎么去查？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你以为我还没有看出你也是个会武功的人，就算你现在是个杂货店老板，以前也一定在江湖中走动过，而且一定是个很有名的人，因为我看得出你武功还不算太差。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "如果你不替我去做这件事，我就……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你就怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我就从现在开始不吃饭，不喝水，反正我早就不想活了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你要我什么时候去？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "现在，现在就去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你可以换身黑衣服，找块黑布蒙着脸，如果被人发现，有人出来追你，你千万不要直接逃回来，我知道你也不想让别人看出你的来历。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你一定要照我的话做，这些事我虽然没有做过，可是有个江湖中的大行家教过我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我宁愿半死不活的躺在这破杂货店里，只因为我相信总有一天有人会来告诉我，这是怎么回事，所以你千万不能让别人找到这里来，否则我们两个都死定了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我错了，我刚才说你以前在江湖中一定是个名人，现在我才知道我错了，江湖中的事，你好像连一点都不懂。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不该看的地方也许去看过了，该看的地方你却没有看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "什么地方是该看的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你到厨房里去看过没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我知道厨房里没有人，为什么还要去看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "去看看灶里最近有没有生过火。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你有没有去看过那口井？井里有没有水？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我为什么要去看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为没有火的灶，没有水的井，都是藏人的好地方，里面，都可能有暗道秘窟。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "教给你这些事的那位大行家，懂得的事并不少。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "现在我已经把这些事教给你了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你是不是还要我去看一次。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你最好现在就去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_nan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "买盐的人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "张老板，你来了么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_nan_ren",
      "text": "我来了！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_nan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "买盐的人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你既然来了，为什么不下来坐坐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_nan_ren",
      "text": "我下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    }
